FBIS4-26346 "drchi119_a_94001" FBIS-CHI-94-119 Daily Report 21 Jun 1994 INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS General Beijing Hopes Koreas Summit Held `At an Early Date' Beijing Hopes Koreas Summit Held `At an Early Date' SK2106084494 Seoul YONHAP in English 0756 GMT 21 Jun 94 SK2106084494 Seoul YONHAP English BFN [Text] Beijing, June 21 (YONHAP) -- The Chinese Government has expressed hope that inter-Korean summit talks would be realized at an early date and produce good results. Noting that both South and North Korea have voiced a desire to hold the summit, a Foreign Ministry spokesman said Tuesday, "We hold this in admiration and hope that the talks would be realized at an early date and produce positive results."
